oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Bernie Terrell and Frankie Wray at the Grand Stand Music Hall (17872)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Terrell, Bernie; Lonzo and Oscar; Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (blue and red on white) announcing a Country Music Revue with Bernie Terrell, Frankie Wray and Lonzo and Oscar at the Grand Strand Music Hall on September 11. Poster features metal photoplates of Bernie Terrell, Frankie Wray, and Lonzo and Oscar. For additional information about this poster see https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/22958.
